                     <interp inst="t17231204-27-off148" type="offenceSubcategory" value="arson"></interp>
               feloniously setting Fire to a Barn of 
                     <persName id="t17231204-27-victim147" type="victimName">
                        Hezekiah 
                        Burr 
                     <interp inst="t17231204-27-victim147" type="surname" value="Burr"></interp>
